title: Complete Genome Sequence of Avian Coronavirus Strain GA08 (GI-27 Lineage)
body: The complete genome sequence of the Avian coronavirus GA/1476/2015 isolate of the GA08 strain has been deposited in GenBank under accession number MN599049. Raw data were deposited under SRA accession number SRR10742650, BioSample number SAMN13088878, and BioProject number PRJNA556282.
